255
00:20:58.796 --> 00:21:00.653
I met with him.

256
00:21:00.653 --> 00:21:03.043
<i>What... is your reason?</i>

257
00:21:03.043 --> 00:21:05.174
Because Ji Soo will grow
more and more uncomfortable

258
00:21:05.174 --> 00:21:07.371
the more she sees me.

259
00:21:07.371 --> 00:21:10.770
<i>And I heard about the accident
that happened 10 years ago.</i>

260
00:21:11.355 --> 00:21:13.126
And then, I knew

261
00:21:13.126 --> 00:21:15.981
who you were looking at
in that photo.

262
00:21:15.981 --> 00:21:17.636
Ji Soo.

263
00:21:18.179 --> 00:21:21.439
Seeing each other will only cause
you two more grief.

264
00:21:21.439 --> 00:21:25.136
Are you sure that you won't be able to
