265
00:21:25.136 --> 00:21:26.601
And what about him?

266
00:21:26.601 --> 00:21:29.221
Do you think he'll be able to avoid
thinking about it while looking at you?

267
00:21:34.874 --> 00:21:36.651
That's why...

268
00:21:37.439 --> 00:21:39.207
you should stay by
my side, like you are now.

269
00:21:39.207 --> 00:21:41.163
I'm not in the mood
to joke around, Senior.

270
00:21:41.163 --> 00:21:43.130
I've never joked around about this.

271
00:21:43.816 --> 00:21:46.538
After confessing to you
ten years ago...

272
00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:49.941
I've always been serious
about my feelings for you.

273
00:21:49.941 --> 00:21:51.774
Senior.

274
00:21:52.359 --> 00:21:54.094
You really didn't know?

275
00:21:54.763 --> 00:21:57.702
Are you sure you didn't just want to
believe that I was joking around?

276
00:22:02.773 --> 00:22:04.795
Let's just say that
I was only joking around, then.

277
00:22:04.795 --> 00:22:07.011
Until you tell me to.

278
00:22:07.683 --> 00:22:09.558
I don't know when
that may be

279
00:22:09.558 --> 00:22:11.923
but I'll wait by your side until then.

280
00:22:11.923 --> 00:22:14.180
Allow me that, at least.

281
00:22:18.396 --> 00:22:20.482
It's almost time.
Let's head inside.

282
00:22:25.223 --> 00:22:27.239
It really is about time now...

283
00:22:27.942 --> 00:22:30.278
for you throw out that photo now,
don't you think?

284
00:22:43.799 --> 00:22:46.480
She said that it's a
7 o' clock flight.

285
00:22:47.143 --> 00:22:48.679
Ugh.

286
00:22:57.207 --> 00:22:59.239
Are you okay, Shin Woo?

287
00:22:59.239 --> 00:23:00.253
Yeah.

288
00:23:03.297 --> 00:23:07.353
You don't know where in the U.S.
Ji Soo went, either?

289
00:23:07.353 --> 00:23:08.603
No.

290
00:23:08.603 --> 00:23:11.373
I only heard that she's
going to the U.S.

291
00:23:11.373 --> 00:23:13.915
How am I supposed
to tell her, then?

292
00:23:19.122 --> 00:23:20.288
Choo Geun Deok!

293
00:23:20.288 --> 00:23:21.610
Why are you here?

294
00:23:21.610 --> 00:23:24.424
There's a photo that you were in,
so I wanted to give it to you.

295
00:23:24.424 --> 00:23:26.068
Here.

296
00:23:26.068 --> 00:23:27.588
Ugh.

297
00:23:28.911 --> 00:23:30.976
Hey, where are you going, Kang Shin Woo?

298
00:23:30.976 --> 00:23:32.962
I have one of you, too.
Take it.

299
00:23:42.680 --> 00:23:43.840
This is...

300
00:23:44.379 --> 00:23:47.258
the photo that I'll have
in ten years, right?

301
00:23:47.258 --> 00:23:50.491
Well, yeah, if you hold
onto it for ten years.

