<i>[It wasn't your fault.]</i>

305
00:24:26.670 --> 00:24:28.363
<i>[It wasn't your fault.]</i>

306
00:24:28.363 --> 00:24:31.171
She'll probably contact me
when she sees...

307
00:24:31.671 --> 00:24:32.794
no.

308
00:24:33.415 --> 00:24:37.583
If I meet with Ji Soo now,
the future will change.

309
00:24:40.065 --> 00:24:41.890
<i>Just know one thing.</i>

310
00:24:42.436 --> 00:24:46.556
<i>I'll come meet you.
