bringing your girlfriend.

489
00:38:21.457 --> 00:38:23.915
My girlfriend is right here, though.

490
00:38:23.915 --> 00:38:24.942
- Huh?
- Huh?

491
00:38:24.942 --> 00:38:27.096
- Who?
