492
00:38:27.096 --> 00:38:29.040
The prettiest woman here.

493
00:38:29.951 --> 00:38:31.846
Oh, jeez.

494
00:38:32.830 --> 00:38:35.424
- Hey, hey, hey.
- Here.

495
00:38:41.433 --> 00:38:44.165
Shin Woo, Shin Woo, Shin Woo!
