496
00:38:44.165 --> 00:38:45.203
- One, two, three!
- One, two, three!

497
00:38:45.203 --> 00:38:46.482
- The hospital!
- Firefly Bridge!

498
00:38:46.482 --> 00:38:47.966
- Come on!
- What was that?

499
00:38:47.966 --> 00:38:50.165
You know, back when you
