500
00:38:50.165 --> 00:38:51.189
- One more time!
- Okay.

501
00:38:51.189 --> 00:38:52.234
A different question, then.

502
00:38:52.234 --> 00:38:54.285
The first time that you two
had physical contact!

503
00:38:54.285 --> 00:38:55.339
One, two, three!

504
00:38:55.339 --> 00:38:56.614
- The schoolyard!
- Firefly Bridge!

505
00:38:56.614 --> 00:38:58.138
What's with you two?

506
00:38:58.138 --> 00:38:59.777
Are you sure you two are dating?

507
00:38:59.777 --> 00:39:01.194
Oh, of course!

508
00:39:01.194 --> 00:39:04.690
I wonder what you did,
and with whom, at Firefly Bridge.

509
00:39:04.690 --> 00:39:05.774
It's weird.

510
00:39:05.774 --> 00:39:08.120
- It's really weird!
- Back then...

511
00:39:08.120 --> 00:39:09.477
with Deok Goo.

512
00:39:09.477 --> 00:39:10.531
Jeez.

513
00:39:10.531 --> 00:39:12.908
Here, have this, Ms. Baek.

514
00:39:13.785 --> 00:39:15.768
Come on, why are you
acting like this?

515
00:39:16.419 --> 00:39:18.207
Stop it!
That's enough.

516
00:39:18.207 --> 00:39:20.033
Let go of me.

517
00:39:27.763 --> 00:39:29.203
Oh!

518
00:39:33.459 --> 00:39:35.435
Stop it, it's hot!

519
00:39:35.435 --> 00:39:37.138
Hey, Kang Shin Woo!

520
00:39:37.138 --> 00:39:38.540
Are you still mad?

521
00:39:40.719 --> 00:39:42.598
Tell me the truth.

522
00:39:42.598 --> 00:39:43.636
About what?

523
00:39:43.636 --> 00:39:45.788
I feel like you liked him more.

524
00:39:45.788 --> 00:39:47.089
You did, didn't you?

525
00:39:48.518 --> 00:39:49.707
Well...

526
00:39:49.707 --> 00:39:53.401
I do think that he was
more my type, yeah.

527
00:39:53.401 --> 00:39:54.712
What?

528
00:39:54.712 --> 00:39:56.629
I'm just kidding!

529
00:39:56.629 --> 00:39:58.125
Why is that even important?

530
00:39:58.125 --> 00:39:59.681
That was all you too, anyway.

531
00:40:03.642 --> 00:40:06.053
- Hurry up and tell him! Do it!
- Hurry!

532
00:40:06.053 --> 00:40:07.542
Teach.

533
00:40:08.049 --> 00:40:09.518
I like you.

534
00:40:10.098 --> 00:40:11.216
Huh?

535
00:40:12.779 --> 00:40:15.265
Teach, she wants you to wait
just one more year for her.

536
00:40:15.265 --> 00:40:17.093
She's serious about it, Teach!

537
00:40:19.116 --> 00:40:20.421
Wow.

538
00:40:20.421 --> 00:40:23.636
How is it that this is the same,
even after ten years?

539
00:40:23.636 --> 00:40:25.431
She's just like you.

540
00:40:26.192 --> 00:40:27.723
This won't do.

541
00:40:27.723 --> 00:40:28.796
Let's go.

542
00:40:29.352 --> 00:40:30.433
Go where?

543
00:40:30.433 --> 00:40:32.431
Hurry up and transfer over to
a boys' high school!

544
00:40:32.431 --> 00:40:34.067
I don't think this place
is a good fit for you.

545
00:40:34.881 --> 00:40:38.515
<i>There are days when we fight
over insignificant things like this.</i>

546
00:40:38.515 --> 00:40:41.631
<i>But each and every moment
that we share together</i>

547
00:40:41.631 --> 00:40:43.781
<i>sparkle and shine
in a blindingly bright way.</i>

548
00:40:44.437 --> 00:40:46.270
What are you thinking about?

549
00:40:48.122 --> 00:40:50.475
I'm wondering about
what you're thinking about.

550
00:40:51.835 --> 00:40:53.663
If, by any chance

551
00:40:53.663 --> 00:40:56.779
the past changes because of
something that Deok Goo does

552
00:40:56.779 --> 00:40:58.962
and our memories change, too...

553
00:40:58.962 --> 00:41:01.312
and so, if we wake up one day

554
00:41:01.312 --> 00:41:03.940
and something has happened to us,
what do we do then?

555
00:41:04.379 --> 00:41:07.676
Like, what if the things you did while
you traveled through time disappear

556
00:41:07.676 --> 00:41:10.038
or our memories disappear?

557
00:41:10.821 --> 00:41:15.319
Or, we're not together
like we are now?

558
00:41:17.801 --> 00:41:19.801
It doesn't matter.

559
00:41:20.328 --> 00:41:22.658
No matter what happens...

560
00:41:22.658 --> 00:41:26.029
I'd meet you as many times as I'd need to

561
00:41:26.029 --> 00:41:28.640
and like you as many times
as I'd need to...

562
00:41:28.640 --> 00:41:30.859
and hold onto you...

563
00:41:31.495 --> 00:41:33.422
as many times as I'd need to.

564
00:41:56.591 --> 00:41:59.709
<i>[2009]</i>

565
00:42:02.247 --> 00:42:03.469
What is it?

566
00:42:03.469 --> 00:42:05.413
My friend attends this school.

567
00:42:05.413 --> 00:42:07.886
Really? Then go see them
before we go.

568
00:42:08.877 --> 00:42:10.518
Not yet.

569
00:42:10.518 --> 00:42:12.536
I can't meet with her yet.

570
00:42:17.942 --> 00:42:19.835
Is anything okay with you?

571
00:42:19.835 --> 00:42:22.259
Well, the weather
is nice and all...

572
00:42:22.259 --> 00:42:23.589
so let's have some alcohol.

573
00:42:31.392 --> 00:42:35.265
<i>[2013]</i>

574
00:42:40.921 --> 00:42:42.326
Yeah, Kim Min Seok.

575
00:42:42.326 --> 00:42:43.634
Where are you?

576
00:42:45.288 --> 00:42:47.013
Ugh, again?

577
00:42:47.013 --> 00:42:49.453
I told you, I'm not going
on any blind dates!

578
00:42:49.453 --> 00:42:50.950
Ugh.

579
00:43:21.261 --> 00:43:22.321
<i>[September 30th, 2017]</i>

580
00:43:22.321 --> 00:43:25.890
<i>And so, one day, after I'd
waited another 10 years...</i>

581
00:43:57.977 --> 00:43:59.834
I missed you...

582
00:44:00.660 --> 00:44:02.071
a lot.

583
00:44:04.234 --> 00:44:07.297
<i>Even when our story
is starting over...</i>

584
00:44:08.107 --> 00:44:10.350
<i>my only answer...</i>

585
00:44:11.100 --> 00:44:12.518
<i>is only you.</i>

586
00:44:17.411 --> 00:44:22.411
Subtitles by DramaFever

